- `GET /api/strategy/double-board/{spot_id}` — stored GTO strategy

### MCCFR Extension
Double board GTO requires:
1. Extended game tree: each infoset includes board context
2. Two simultaneous evaluations per leaf
3. Pot splits computed at terminal nodes
4. CFR updates on both boards independently

**Performance note:** Double board MCCFR is ~2× slower than single board (two evaluations per leaf).

